        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="70" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
When you log on, what is it you do that makes you glad your a Necromancer? 

As a lowbie I enjoyed being able to pile on the DoTs, knowing it would take 3 minutes, but I might take out a Red con. 

Now that I'm approaching the high end, I like the being able to cast nearly non stop, and being able to run into nearly any situation with a fair chance of escaping, no matter how rough it gets.

Whats your favorite things about being a Necromancer?

 
[/quote]</textarea><br>
